{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-post-js","path":"/fluxstore/currency-switcher/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://docs.inspireui.com","title":"InspireUI Document","description":"InspireUI document"}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Common Features","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"FluxStore - Universal mobile commerce Flutter app for Magento, WooCommerce and Opencart","meta_description":"Fluxstore is universal app that fully integration with the Woocommerce, Mangeto and Opencart","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"fluxstore","toc":null,"keywords":["fluxstore","flutter app","fluxstore","Magento app","Woo Commerce app","Opencart app"]},"html":"<article class=\"flex-auto pa5 pa8-m pa15-l pt10-ns pb10-ns pt10-l pb10-l relative\">\n<section class=\"post-content external-scripts\">\n<p><strong>Compatible with</strong>: <a href=\"https://1.envato.market/1jq76\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">FluxStore WooCommerce</a>, <a href=\"https://1.envato.market/40oN3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">FluxStore Pro</a>, <a href=\"https://1.envato.market/NW4q1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">FluxStore MultiVendor</a> apps<br><strong>License required</strong>: All Licenses.<br><strong>Product version: </strong>+1.8.0</p>\n<p>This section shows how to config Multi currencies, Default \u001dcurrency.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-multi-currencies-setting\" style=\"position: relative;\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"></svg>1. Multi Currencies Setting</h2>\n<p><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px;\"> <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" style=\"display: block;\" href=\"/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/5dbd9/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; opacity: 0;\" title=\"fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter\" src=\"/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/29d74/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/b4ec0/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 200w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/24144/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 400w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/29d74/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 800w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/5c837/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 1200w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/db573/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 1600w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/5dbd9/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 2880w\" alt=\"fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter\"> </a> </span></p>\n<p>This feature is only available for the WooCommerce version (FluxStore WooCommerce, FluxStore Pro(Woo), FluxStore MultiVendor apps). Here are the required conditions to activate this feature:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Update the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mstore-api/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">mstore-api</a> to the latest version <strong>v1.5.4.</strong></li>\n<li>Add new setting from <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/related-projects/woocommerce-multilingual/multi-currency-support-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Manage Currencies from WPML plugin</a>:</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px;\"> <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" style=\"display: block;\" href=\"/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/0e5af/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; opacity: 0;\" title=\"IMG_1790fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui\" src=\"/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/29d74/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/b4ec0/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 200w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/24144/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 400w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/29d74/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 800w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/5c837/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 1200w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/db573/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 1600w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/0e5af/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 2284w\" alt=\"IMG_1790fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui\"> </a> </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Open the Fluxstore project, and update the <code>lib/env.dart</code> and update the <code>Currencies</code> value. (For version 1.9.x and earlier, refer to lib/common/config/general.dart with kAdvanceConfig).</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\">\n<pre class=\"language-json\"><code>\"advanceConfig\": {\n  ...\n  \"Currencies\": [\n    {\n      \"symbol\": \"\\$\",\n      \"decimalDigits\": 2,\n      \"symbolBeforeTheNumber\": true,\n      \"currency\": \"USD\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"symbol\": \"Ä‘\",\n      \"decimalDigits\": 2,\n      \"symbolBeforeTheNumber\": true,\n      \"currency\": \"VND\"\n    }\n  ]\n},</code></pre>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"2-default-currency\" style=\"position: relative;\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"></svg>2. Default Currency</h2>\n<p>Open <strong><code>lib/env.dart</code></strong> file and update the <code class=\"language-text\">DefaultCurrency</code> section. (For version 1.9.x and earlier, refer to lib/common/config/general.dart with kAdvanceConfig).</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\">\n<pre class=\"language-json\"><code>  \"advanceConfig\": {\n  ...\n    \"DefaultCurrency\": {\n      \"symbol\": \"\\$\",\n      \"decimalDigits\": 2,\n      \"symbolBeforeTheNumber\": true,\n      \"currency\": \"USD\",\n      \"currencyCode\": \"usd\",\n      \"smallestUnitRate\": 100, // 100 cents = 1 usd\n    },\n  ...\n  },</code></pre>\n</div>\n</section>\n</article>","fields":{"slug":"/fluxstore/currency-switcher/"},"timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/minh/Data/Projects/web/inspireui-document/content/fluxstore/currency-switcher.md"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/fluxstore/currency-switcher/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}